                                                              Sending/Receiving problem notification

It would be useful to have a alerting mechanism in place that would notify us about important events even when we are not directly looking at Zabbix frontend.

Steps to configure an alert via Email.

E-mail settings
    Go to Administration → Media types 
    Click on Email in the list of pre-defined media types.
    Set the values of SMTP server, SMTP helo and SMTP e-mail to the appropriate for your environment.
    Press Update.


New action
    To set up a notification, go to Configuration → Actions 
    Click on Create action.
    Compled the Actions and Operations form details 
    Click Add

Receiving notification
    We should receive a problem notification in your e-mail
